data.description:
Adorable home in a convenient location. This charming 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence with 2 car attached garage on the west side of town offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Step inside to discover a warm and inviting interior, featuring a spacious living area with a wood fireplace insert, formal dining room, 3 bedrooms with 2 bathrooms.
Downstairs you will find a second family room, laundry and 2 non conforming bedrooms, full bath and plenty of storage area. 
One of the highlights of this home is its proximity to the park, providing a picturesque view out your front windows.  Imagine enjoying morning strolls or picnics in the park, just steps away from your front door.

Call Amber Giulio 406-439-8816 or your real estate professional for your showing today.
